('4ff943b2-f1fc-59e1-8d5c-47443aac007d', '503bfce3-13aa-4f34-abf9-cab0bce512f9', 'Please wash your hands ___ dinner.', '請在晚餐之前洗手。', 'before', 'after', 'with', 'during', 'fore 表示『在前面』，加上 be 構成 before。', 'be (在) + fore (前) → before (在...之前)', '2026-07-07 03:08:42', '2026-07-07 03:08:42'),
('0337965d-3e7d-55cc-a6da-7970c690ded1', '9ae63574-9125-4c90-9e15-8e31ce2d7c72', 'The teacher uses ___ to write the math problems on the blackboard.', '老師用粉筆在黑板上寫數學題。', 'chalk', 'pencil', 'eraser', 'marker', 'chalk 為名詞，指粉筆。', '想像老師在黑板上寫字時，那種『擦擦』的聲音 → chalk 粉筆', '2026-07-07 03:05:44', '2026-07-07 03:05:44'),
('82003517-5bde-5983-a62e-12eab637d379', 'e43588d7-5b1e-478a-a386-17fc2467ba4b', 'My mother cooked some delicious ___ for dinner tonight.', '我媽媽今晚晚餐煮了一些好吃的雞肉。', 'chicken', 'beef', 'bread', 'apple', 'chicken → 雞或雞肉 (名詞)', '想像在餐廳點餐時，看到美味雞肉料理的樣子。', '2026-07-07 03:39:05', '2026-07-07 03:39:05'),
('b623588d-7943-5645-b3d8-f24deb6428f9', 'e43588d7-5b1e-478a-a386-17fc2467ba4b', 'Look! There are many small ___ running on the farm.', '看！農場上有許多小雞在跑。', 'chickens', 'cows', 'ducks', 'dogs', 'chicken → 雞 (名詞)，在此情境下需用複數 chickens', '想像小雞在農場跑來跑去，發出雞叫聲。', '2026-07-07 03:39:05', '2026-07-07 03:39:05'),
